**Reasoning:**

Alice is clearly trying to take advantage of the situation, and her offers are getting worse for me with each round.  While time is running out, I need to hold firm. Accepting a deal where I get significantly less than half, even with the inflation, sets a bad precedent and signals I'm desperate.  There's a chance Alice will panic as we get closer to the deadline and offer something more reasonable.
